OL,3,CAttorney general 'considering' jail
OL,4,Csentence of Henry Nowak's murderer
OL,6,FThe attorney general's office is
OL,7,Fconsidering the jail sentence given to
OL,8,FVickrum Digwa after receiving
OL,9,F"multiple requests" to review it under
OL,10,Fthe unduly lenient sentence (ULS)
OL,11,Fscheme.
OL,13,FThe 23-year-old was sentenced to life
OL,14,Fto serve a minimum of 21 years at
OL,15,FSouthampton Crown Court for the murder
OL,16,Fof 18-year-old Henry Nowak.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@SO]
