OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780441387
OL,3,CAttorney general 'considering' jail
OL,4,Csentence of Henry Nowak's murderer
OL,6,FA spokesman for his office said: "We
OL,7,Fhave received multiple requests for
OL,8,FVickrum Digwa's sentence to be
OL,9,Fconsidered under the unduly lenient
OL,10,Fsentence (ULS) scheme.
OL,12,F"The law officers have 28 days from
OL,13,Fsentencing to carefully consider the
OL,14,Fcase and make a decision."
OL,16,FDigwa stabbed the finance student five
OL,17,Ftimes with a 21cm blade that he said
OL,18,Fhe carried as part of his Sikh faith.
OL,20,FIt happened on Belmont Road,
OL,21,FSouthampton, on December 3, 2025.
OL,26,@nD@bOUtD@AOUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
