OL,3,CAttorney general 'considering' jail
OL,4,Csentence of Henry Nowak's murderer
OL,6,FIn England and Wales, murder carries a
OL,7,Fmandatory life sentence with a
OL,8,Fstarting point of 15 years.
OL,10,FThe starting point is 25 years if a
OL,11,Fknife or weapon was taken to the scene
OL,12,Fwith intent to commit a crime, but
OL,13,FJudge William Mousley KC said that did
OL,14,Fnot apply to the case.
OL,16,FHe told the sentencing hearing at
OL,17,FSouthampton Crown Court: "The murder
OL,18,Fdid not involve taking a knife to the
OL,19,Fscene with the purpose to use it to
OL,20,Fcommit an offence or to have it
OL,21,Favailable to do so.
OL,26,@yD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
