OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780441387
OL,3,CAttorney general 'considering' jail
OL,4,Csentence of Henry Nowak's murderer
OL,6,F"It is possible that (Digwa) had a
OL,7,Fgood legal reason for having the
OL,8,Fdagger when you met Henry although,
OL,9,Fconsidering the jury's verdict, that
OL,10,Freason must have come to an end after
OL,11,Fyou removed it from its sheath."
OL,13,FJudge Mousley moved the minimum term
OL,14,Fup to 23 years because of "a number of
OL,15,Faggravating factors", before settling
OL,16,Fon 21 years taking into account
OL,17,Fmitigating factors such as Digwa's age
OL,18,Fand good record.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@`O]vD@[OUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780441387
OL,3,CAttorney general 'considering' jail
OL,4,Csentence of Henry Nowak's murderer
OL,6,FHe also jailed him for two years for
OL,7,Fcarrying a knife in public, to run
OL,8,Fconcurrently to the murder count.
OL,10,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,11,FConduct said investigators are
OL,12,Fexamining a large amount of police
OL,13,Fbody-worn video as well as material
OL,14,Fpresented during the trial.
OL,16,FA spokesperson said: "Our thoughts and
OL,17,Fsympathies are with Henry Nowak's
OL,18,Ffamily and everyone affected by his
OL,19,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
