OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780441387
OL,3,CAttorney general 'considering' jail
OL,4,Csentence of Henry Nowak's murderer
OL,6,F"We are independently investigating
OL,7,Fthe contact Hampshire and Isle of
OL,8,FWight officers had with Mr Nowak prior
OL,9,Fto his death on 4 December, including
OL,10,Fthe use of handcuffs by officers and
OL,11,Fthe first aid provided.
OL,13,F"Our investigation, which began
OL,14,Ffollowing a mandatory referral from
OL,15,Fthe force that we received the same
OL,16,Fday, remains ongoing and the officers
OL,17,Finvolved are currently being treated
OL,18,Fas witnesses."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
